{"descriptions":[{"authors":[{"fullname":"Nicolas Tournadre","id":"6"}],"source_url":null,"content":"<p class=\"Paragraph\">Numbers come after the noun. Unlike Burmese, Chinese, and several other Asian languages, Tibetan has no classifiers.</p> <table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(0) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༠</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཀླད་ཀོར་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(1) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༡</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཅིག་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(2) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༢</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཉིས་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(3) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༣</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གསུམ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(4) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༤</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཞི་</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(5) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༥</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལྔ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(6) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༦</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དྲུག</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(7) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༧</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བདུན་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(8) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༨</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱད་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(9) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༩</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དགུ</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(10) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༡༠</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(11) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༡༡</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་གཅིག་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(12) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༡༢</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་གཉིས་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(13) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༡༣</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་གསུམ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(14) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༡༤</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་བཞི་</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(15) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༡༥</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅོ་ལྔ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(16) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༡༦</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་དྲུག་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(17) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༡༧</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་བདུན་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(18) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༡༨</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅོ་བརྒྱད་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"95\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(19) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༡༩</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་དགུ་</span></p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Between 20 and 90, each set of ten makes use of a special particle:</p> <table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྩ་</span> (20)</p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སོ་</span> (30)</p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཞེ་</span> (40)</p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ང་</span> (50)</p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རེ་</span> (60)</p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དོན་</span> (70)</p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གྱ་</span> (80)</p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གོ་</span> (90)</p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Remembering these particles is made easier by the fact that, with the exception of <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">རྩ་</span>, they are all derived from the term for the set of ten in question. For example, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སོ་</span>, the particle for the thirties, is derived from <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གསུམ་</span> &ldquo;three.&rdquo; The same is true of the forties, where <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཞེ་</span> is a modification of <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཞི་</span> &ldquo;four,&rdquo; and so on.</p> <table border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"> <tbody> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(20) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༢༠</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉི་ཤུ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(21) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༢༡</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉི་ཤི་རྩ་གཅིག་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;through</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(29) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༢༩</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉི་ཤི་རྩ་དགུ་</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(30) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༣༠</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སུམ་ཅུ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(31) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༣༡</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སུམ་ཅུ་སོ་གཅིག་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">through</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(39) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༣༩</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སུམ་ཅུ་སོ་དགུ་</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(40) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༤༠</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཞི་བཅུ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(41) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༤༡</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཞི་བཅུ་ཞེ་བཅིག་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">through</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(49) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༤༩</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཞི་བཅུ་ཞེ་དགུ་</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(50) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༥༠</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལྔ་བཅུ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(51) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༥༡</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལྔ་བཅུ་ང་གཅིག་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">through</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(59) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༥༩</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ལྔ་བཅུ་ང་དགུ་</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(60) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༦༠</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དྲུག་བཅུ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(61) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༦༡</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དྲུག་བཅུ་རེ་གཅིག་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">through</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(69) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༦༩</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དྲུག་བཅུ་རེ་དགུ་</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(70) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༧༠</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བདུན་བཅུ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(71) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༧༡</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བདུན་བཅུ་དོན་གཅིག་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">through</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(79) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༧༩</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བདུན་བཅུ་དོན་དགུ་</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(80) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༨༠</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱད་ཅུ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(81) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༨༡</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱད་ཅུ་གྱ་གཅིག་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">through</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(89) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༨༩</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱད་ཅུ་གྱ་དགུ་</span></p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(90) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༩༠</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དགུ་བཅུ་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">&nbsp;</p> </td> </tr> <tr> <td width=\"96\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(91) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༩༡</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དགུ་བཅུ་གོ་གཅིག་</span></p> </td> <td width=\"64\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">through</p> </td> <td width=\"87\" valign=\"top\"> <p class=\"Paragraph\">(99) <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">༩༩</span></p> <p class=\"Paragraph\"><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དགུ་བཅུ་གོ་དགུ་</span></p> </td> </tr> </tbody> </table> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Formation of hundreds uses the word <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱ་</span> &ldquo;hundred&rdquo;:</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆིག་བརྒྱ་</span> &ldquo;One hundred&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉིས་བརྒྱ་</span> &ldquo;Two hundred&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སུམ་བརྒྱ་</span> &ldquo;Three hundred,&rdquo; and so forth</li> </ul> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Between 100 and 199, the number &ldquo;hundred&rdquo; is followed by the connective <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དང་</span> &ldquo;and.&rdquo; (Between 200 and 999 <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དང་</span> is optional and is usually dropped.) For example:</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱ་དང་ལྔ་བཅུ་</span> &ldquo;One hundred fifty&rdquo; </li> </ul> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Formation of thousands uses <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྟོང་</span> &ldquo;thousand&rdquo;:</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆིག་སྟོང་</span> &ldquo;One thousand&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉིས་སྟོང་</span> &ldquo;Two thousand&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སུམ་སྟོང་</span> &ldquo;Three thousand&rdquo;</li> </ul> <p class=\"Paragraph\">For ten thousands, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁྲི་</span> &ldquo;ten thousand&rdquo; is used:</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆིག་ཁྲི་</span> &ldquo;One myriad&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉིས་ཁྲི་</span> &ldquo;Twenty thousand (two myriad)&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སུམ་ཁྲི་</span> &ldquo;Thirty thousand&rdquo;</li> </ul> <p class=\"Paragraph\">For hundred thousands, <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འབུམ་</span> &ldquo;hundred thousand&rdquo; is used:</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆིག་འབུམ་</span> &ldquo;One (unit of a) hundred thousand,&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉིས་འབུམ་</span> &ldquo;Two hundred thousand&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སུམ་འབུམ་</span> &ldquo;Three hundred thousand&rdquo;</li> </ul> <p class=\"Paragraph\">After &ldquo;million,&rdquo; the numbers are treated as substantives and must be followed (not preceded) by the number of units.</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ས་ཡ་</span> &ldquo;Million&rdquo;: <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ས་ཡ་གཅིག་</span> &ldquo;One million,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ས་ཡ་གཉིས་</span> &ldquo;Two million,&rdquo; and so forth. </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེ་བ་</span> &ldquo;Ten million&rdquo;: <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེ་བ་གཅིག་</span> &ldquo;(One unit of) ten million,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བྱེ་བ་གཉིས་</span> &ldquo;Twenty million,&rdquo; and so forth. </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དུང་ཕྱུར་</span> &ldquo;Hundred million&rdquo;: <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དུང་ཕྱུར་གཅིག་</span> &ldquo;(One unit of a) hundred million,&rdquo; <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དུང་ཕྱུར་གཉིས་</span> &ldquo;Two hundred million,&rdquo; and so forth. </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དུང་ཕྱུར་བཅུ་</span> &ldquo;One billion.&rdquo; </li> </ul> <p class=\"Paragraph\">From a hundred up to a hundred thousand, units may be placed afterward, and the number is therefore treated syntactically as a substantive. In the case of &ldquo;thousand,&rdquo; the suffix <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཕྲག་</span> is added:</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སྟོང་ཕྲག་གཉིས་</span> &ldquo;Two thousand&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཁྲི་གསུམ་</span> &ldquo;Thirty thousand&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">འབུམ་གསུམ་</span> &ldquo;Three hundred thousand&rdquo;</li> </ul> <p class=\"Paragraph\">From one hundred up, when there is a zero in the tens, hundreds, or any higher column, as in 108 or 1015, the column name (10, 100, etc.) is followed by <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">མེད་</span> &ldquo;without.&rdquo; This expression is optional:</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆིག་སྟོང་བཞི་བརྒྱ་བཅུ་མེད་བདུན་</span> &ldquo;1407&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆིག་སྟོང་བརྒྱ་མེད་བཅུ་དྲུག་</span> &ldquo;1016&rdquo;</li> </ul> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Note: The numbers 1, 2, 3, and 10 are spelled differently according to the other numbers with which they are combined, as in the case of 15 (10+5), 18 (10+8), 20 (2x10), 30 (3x10), etc. The written variants represent a formalization, from the classical period, of different pronunciations of the numbers in question.</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཅིག་</span> is spelled <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆིག་</span> in <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆིག་སྟོང་</span> &ldquo;1000&rdquo;</li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཉིས་</span> is spelled <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉི་</span> in <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉི་ཤུ་</span> &ldquo;20&rdquo;</li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཉིས་</span> is spelled <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉིས་</span> in <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉིས་སྟོང་</span> &ldquo;2000&rdquo;</li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གསུམ་</span> is spelled <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སུམ་</span> in <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སུམ་ཅུ་</span> &ldquo;30&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་</span> is spelled <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅོ་</span> in <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅོ་ལྔ་</span> &ldquo;15&rdquo; and <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅོ་བརྒྱད་</span> &ldquo;18&rdquo;</li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་</span> is spelled <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཤུ</span> in <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཉི་ཤུ་</span> &ldquo;20&rdquo;</li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་</span> is spelled <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཅུ་</span> in <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སུམ་ཅུ་</span> &ldquo;30&rdquo; and in <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དྲུག་ཅུ་</span> &ldquo;60,&rdquo; etc. </li> </ul> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Note that round tens and hundreds may be followed by <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཐམ་པ་</span>. For example:</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱ་ཐམ་པ་</span> &ldquo;A hundred&rdquo;</li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">སུམ་ཅུ་ཐམ་པ་</span> &ldquo;Thirty&rdquo;</li> </ul> <p class=\"Paragraph\">Ordinal numbers present no difficulties. With the exception of &ldquo;first,&rdquo; which has a special radical, they are formed simply by adding the suffix <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">པ་</span>. For example:</p> <ul> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">དང་པོ་</span> &ldquo;First&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གཉིས་པ་</span> &ldquo;Second&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གསུམ་པ་</span> &ldquo;Third&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་པ་</span> &ldquo;Tenth&rdquo; </li> <li><span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཅུ་གཅིག་པ་</span> &ldquo;Eleventh,&rdquo; and so forth</li> </ul> <p class=\"Paragraph\">The percentages and fractions are formed by using the word <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">ཆ་</span> &ldquo;part.&rdquo; Thus:</p> <ul> <li>One hundred percent <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱ་ཆ་བརྒྱ་</span></li> <li>Fifty percent <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བརྒྱ་ཆ་ལྔ་བཅུ་</span></li> <li>One third <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">གསུམ་ཆ་གཅིག་</span></li> <li>Three quarters <span class=\"tibetan\" title=\"Type ID here\">བཞི་ཆ་གསུམ་</span></li> </ul>","created_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:24 UTC","updated_at":"2013-09-15 04:15:24 UTC","id":1277,"title":null,"is_primary":true}]}